title: Beautiful 55+ 1 BR Apartment Home! This One Definitely Won’t Last!
posting_body: ['The Legends of Spring Lake Park, a active 55+ living community, is where quality & affordability meet.', 'Enjoy the comforts of maintenance-free living along with the convenience of an outstanding location.', 'These spacious 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartments feature a full-size washer & dryer, separate dining & living room spaces & gorgeous kitchen cabinetry with breakfast bar or center island.', 'You’ll also enjoy spectacular views from your personal patio or balcony.', 'Finally…', 'It’s time to reserve your dream home today!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Sleek & Modern Wood Kitchen Cabinetry with Granite Countertops', '- Full-Size Washer & Dryer', 'In EVERY Home!', '- Professional On-Site Management Team', '- Close to Numerous Dining, Shopping & Entertainment Options!', '- Open & Spacious Floorplans', '- Kitchen Breakfast Bar or Island', '- Outdoor Patio & Grilling Areas', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Spring Lake Park is an active 55+ living community that participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Spring Lake Park', '1066 County Highway 10 NE', 'Spring Lake Park, MN, 55432', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'H9fQpc3Uk']
